			<h4><a name="2196720">Re:The present and the future</a></h4>


		 	<span id="comment_score_2196720" class="score">(Score:2)</span>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			by <a href="//slashdot.org/~nathanh">nathanh (1214)</a> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_2196720">		
		on Monday August 20, @06:55AM (<a href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=20503&amp;cid=2196720">#2196720</a>)
		<small><br>(<a href="http://www.manu.com.au/" rel="nofollow">http://www.manu.com.au/</a>) </small>
