		 	<span id="comment_score_2213483" class="score">(Score:1)</span>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			by <a href="//slashdot.org/~paulmoham">paulmoham (517600)</a> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_2213483">		
